Package final1.subtests

The actual tests for the programming lecture's final task.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicCommandTest
    Starts the program with either a simple one-line input file or the task sheet input file.
    EdgesCommandTest
    Performs calls to the edges command and checks the results.
    ExportCommandTest
    Performs calls to the export command and checks the results.
    InvalidCommandLineArgumentsTest
    Calls the tested class' main method with illegal arguments.
    InvalidInputFileTest
    Starts the program with several invalid input files without performing any actions.
    InvalidRecommendTerms
    Launches the program with a valid input file and then tests some illegal recommend commands.
    RecommendationSubtest
    Base class for implementing subtest for the programming lecture's first final task.
    ValidInputFileTest
    Starts the program with several valid input files without performing any actions.
    ValidNodesCommandTest
    Performs valid calls to the nodes command and checks the results.
    ValidRecommendCommandTest
    Performs valid calls to the recommend command and checks the results.
